column5: Congrats I’m super proud of you! Stay strong . Feel free to dm me if you need anyone to talk to ❤️
Use in your flashlight until the power comes back on. Keep calling the police it’s got to work eventually !
Congratulations I’m so proud of you!

I know you feel like it’s not going to get any better and maybe you’re right but you should stay and see . I’ve been through some rough patches and I could’ve used some help , I can’t go back and change that but I can give help however I can to people who feel now like I did then. My names tori  feel free to dm me or shoot me a text. Here’s my number (506)-608-9164 I’d love to help you out however I can.
Congratulations I’m so proud of you

I creeped your profile and saw your dress. I think you look beautiful and although you would like to make your mother happy it is YOUR big day, not hers . You don’t need to worry about anyone else’s opinion on your dress , it’s your body and you are going to be wearing it. You look gorgeous don’t let your mother tell you otherwise. The dress is very flattering , idk why she was suggesting plus size . I hope your wedding goes wonderful and that she calms down and can act like a mother should. ❤️
I’m so proud of you! ❤️I hope all goes well 2020 , good luck!
I did delete them and I went through every photo place I could to check.
Good luck! Keep us posted on how your surgery goes.
Thank you that gives me hope
